de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database

Class DbScenarioInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbObject
      • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbScenarioInstance

  • public class DbScenarioInstance
extends DbObject
    This class administrates the scenario instances in the databases and provides check methods to make sure the database is correct. Moreover it is possible to mark a scenario instance as terminated.
